152 JOBS~

Avatars: (153)
The Job of the Avatars is to keep the game moving...help with Newbies and being
a overall friendly person.

Angels: (154)
Angels have two main roles: reimbursement and quest running.  Be skeptical
on reimburses, don't just hand out every piece of gear.  I suggest limiting
reimbursements to 10 items at a time, and make sure that you do not load things
at too high a level (new format items have hard-coded levels, so are not a
problem).  vnum and stat are useful for this.  You can draft Avatars to help you
run a quest, and please note that quests should NOT have huge rewards -- the
main point should be to have fun. 

Demigods-Creators: (155-159)
Gods have the roles of keeping the peace. They must make sure that the Mud
is kept bug free and also perform as the other gods do. More is required 
out of these levels than normal. Use your head folks. If your head becomes
too big for you I am sure we can arrange a demotion or two.

Not fullfilling the roles of your office can result in demotion or deletion.
~

