goddess. Many followers of a sect find themselves embowed with special rewards
set by the god or godess. For one special person in each sect a placement of
high honor is granted. This certain honor has a name that each sect god or      goddess names. For some that is the name of High Priest. 
	Many special powers are granted to the Honored person of each sect.
One such thing is the special items they receive and the ability to vote on
many important aspects of the sect. Joining a sect is a big step and one must
be of level 15 or higher before being allowed to join one.
	Some sects will let you buy special rooms and mobs by acquring diamonds
as payment. To see room prices see 'help prices.' To find out more about a 
certain god or goddess simply type 'help <god/dessname>' Example: help variant.
For a complete listing of the gods and goddesses of TSR see 'help pantheon'.
